title: Ep 96 - Expectations Dictate Results
itunes:title: Ep 96 - Expectations Dictate Results
description:
In this episode I talk about how teachers expectations of their students will dictate their students results. If that is the case then how else can expectations dictate results in our lives? I dive into that topic much more in depth.
